original_title: The Fab Five: The King's Grandchildren
overview: As proud grandparents, Charles and Camilla have ten grandchildren between them. While some of them are princes and princesses, others have lives outside the media spotlight. Explores these grandchildren and the complex family they belong to.
tagline: We explore how our new King and Queen will navigate the dynamics of a very modern family.
title: The Fab Five: The King's Grandchildren
